OL,3,CMP says factory possible closure is a
OL,4,C'hammer blow' to workers
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway MP John Cooper
OL,7,Fsays the possible closure of the last
OL,8,FInterfloor factory is a 'hammer blow'
OL,9,Fto workers.
OL,11,FInterfloor, a carpet underlay
OL,12,Fsupplier, which used to be a major
OL,13,Femployer in Dumfries, will now have to
OL,14,Fmake their remaining 30 members of
OL,15,Fstaff redundant, blaming the impact of
OL,16,FUK sanctions on Russia for their
OL,17,Fexpected closure.
