OL,6,FConservative Dumfries and Galloway MP
OL,7,FJohn Cooper says the potential job
OL,8,Flosses are 'devastating' but added the
OL,9,Fsanctions on Russia remain essential
OL,10,Fdespite the cost to businesses.
OL,12,FHe said: "Unfortunately, I think we
OL,13,Fhave got to press back against Russia
OL,14,Fand it's very difficult, there is a
OL,15,Fprice to pay.
