OL,6,F"And all of us, one way or another,
OL,7,Fhave paid that price, for instance,
OL,8,Fpower bills soaring and that's
OL,9,Fdirectly linked to Putin. But I think
OL,10,Fwe do have to push back as best we can
OL,11,Fagainst that."
