OL,3,CMP says factory possible closure is a
OL,4,C'hammer blow' to workers
OL,6,FAlan Ritchie, GMB Scotland, said: "We
OL,7,Fgot a call saying that the company
OL,8,Fwishes to start a consultation period,
OL,9,Fand they have sent letters to the
OL,10,Fworkers saying that they had some
OL,11,Fmajor problems regarding the future of
OL,12,Fthe site.
OL,14,F"I went down to the company last week
OL,15,Fand they told us that they've started
OL,16,Fthe consultation period. This has been
OL,17,Fa major shock to our members."
