OL,3,CMP says factory possible closure is a
OL,4,C'hammer blow' to workers
OL,6,FIn a statement, Interfloor said the
OL,7,Fsite's long-term viability has been
OL,8,Faffected by the "loss of a key raw
OL,9,Fmaterial previously supplied from
OL,10,FRussia".
OL,12,FGary McEwan, Managing Director, said:
OL,13,F"This supply ceased as a result of UK
OL,14,Fsanctions in 2022. Although we have
OL,15,Fsecured alternative sources, the
OL,16,Fsignificantly increased costs have
OL,17,Faffected our competitiveness,
OL,18,Fparticularly in a market also
OL,19,Finfluenced by lower-cost imports.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
