OL,3,CMP says factory possible closure is a
OL,4,C'hammer blow' to workers
OL,6,F"Over the past few years, this
OL,7,Fsituation has led to a marked
OL,8,Freduction in sales, and we have been
OL,9,Foperating at a loss.
OL,11,F"Despite hoping for improvements in
OL,12,Fthe supply chain, there has been no
OL,13,Findication that this will happen in
OL,14,Fthe foreseeable future.
