OL,6,F"As a result, we have entered into a
OL,7,Fformal consultation process with
OL,8,Femployees regarding the future of the
OL,9,Fsite. While these consultations are
OL,10,Fongoing, it would not be appropriate
OL,11,Fto provide further details. Our
OL,12,Fprimary focus remains on supporting
OL,13,Four employees during this difficult
OL,14,Ftime."
